high_descs: turn left and walk to the small white table at the end of the room
grab the spatula off of the table
turn right and walk over to the stove at the end of the room
place the spatula inside of the sauce pan on the stove
pick up the sauce pan off of the stove
turn right and move to the kitchen counter above the dishwasher
place the sauce pan on the kitchen counter in front of you
anns.task_desc: place a sauce pan with a spatula in it on top of the kitchen counter

high_descs: Turn left, then turn right to go to the square table.
Pick up the spatula on the table, to the right of the apple.
Turn left, go straight to the stove.
Place the spatula on the pan, on the stove.
Pick up the pan on the stove.
Turn right, then turn left to face the counter to the right of the sink.
Place the pan on the counter, to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a spatula in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left and begin walking to the door, then hang a right and walk over to the small white table.
Pick up the spatula that is closest to the loaf of bread on the white table.
Turn right walk over to the oven.
Put the spatula handle up in the metal pan on the front left burner of the stove.
Pick up the metal pan with the spatula in it off of the stove.
Turn right and walk over to the section of counter to the right of the sink.
Place the metal pan with the spatula inside of it on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a metal pan with a spatula in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left and head toward the door, then hang a right and walk to the table
Pick up the spatula that is next to the apple
Turn to the right and head to the stove
Place the spatula into the skillet that is on your left
Pick up the skillet that contains the spatula
Turn right and and head to the counter that's to the right of the sink
Place the skillet on the counter to the right of the sink
anns.task_desc: Place a skillet with a spatula on the counter
